Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,\Nyour uniqueness into strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get lost, let’s start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really happy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you're always meeting\Nto someone's expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you change to\Nwho you really wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you always have a great smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of only “the beginning,”\NI wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and someday, I'll live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:01:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, precious things are never in shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what it is\Nwhen you get it or lose it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,\Nyour uniqueness into strength
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get lost,\Nlet's start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what’s up, Temari?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s close. He’s just right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it! What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion…\NPerhaps it was a trap set for Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:03:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry…\NHe wouldn’t get bumped off so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, shall we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, I must have you both\Nreturn to your original forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please prepare yourself,\NSarutobi Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Unrivaled Match:\NHokage Battle Royale!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With every moment,\Nthey are looking more lively…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that…Jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reanimation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a Forbidden Summoning Jutsu\Nthat can bring the dead back to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cost of a regular Summoning Jutsu\Nis that it uses the blood of the caster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I’ve heard that with this Jutsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to summon\Na dead soul to this world…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the body of a living person is sacrificed\Nas a container for the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the bodies of those two\Nare of the sacrificed…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps dust and dirt cover\Nthe sacrificial body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take on the original form\Nof the summoned soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And by way of the charm\Nembedded in the head,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the personality of the soul is killed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it morphs into no more\Nthan a killing puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look like how they used\Nto look more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the joy and sense\Nof accomplishment
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of hurting one whom\Nyou once called Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared this scenario\Nso that you might know that joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the shape and form\Nare the same…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they’re neither the First Hokage\Nnor the Second!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I…know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Style: Fire Dragon Flame Bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Style: Water Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to set into motion that level\Nof Water Style in a place with no water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True to the title of the previous Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Style: Water Shock Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Style: Mud Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same mighty strength as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having two of you is quite a challenge,\Nas might be expected…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Hidden Jutsu of the First Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden Wood Style Jutsu:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep Forest Emergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Chakra became a source for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow… So this is the legendary\NWood Style Ninjutsu of the First Hokage
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who brought turbulent times under control\Nand built the Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re finally caught…eh, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Everyone’s here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay everyone, let’s evacuate quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t rush and don’t panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Konohamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does your stomach hurt or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…it’s not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Summoning Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey King Enma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph…\NSomething pesky has appeared, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old Monkey Enma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru…\NI knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re pathetic, Sarutobi…\Nlt’s because you didn’t kill him back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please…Enma!\NThe Adamantine Nyoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of him.\NDon’t let him transform into that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay… Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow… What level of Ninjutsu battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hokage level!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well…\NThings have finally gotten interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of his Snake Swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s do it, Enma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how strong the body,\Nthe Snake Sword still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So foolish…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you’d strike without even\Nusing the Shadow Clone Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that’s not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that he didn't use it.\NHe can’t use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The amount of Chakra the Third Hokage\Nhas differs from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shadow Clone Jutsu that\Nevenly disperses Chakra,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if things go wrong,\Nwould be like throwing away Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure enough, is it age?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are called…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“the Professor who knows and uses all\Nof the Jutsu existent in Leaf Village,” right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don’t disappoint me too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get up, Lord Hokage…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And please save the Leaf Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool… It is too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarutobi, what’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s as if you’re good for nothing…\NWhat are you hesitating for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now’s the time to draw the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You…fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll snap your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there’s no point if\NI don’t do something about the soul itself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is bound by the Reanimation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:19:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, all I can do is to use…\Nthe Fourth Hokage’s Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord First Hokage, Lord Second Hokage,\Nplease forgive me for using that Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei…it seems you’re out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve gotten old, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never seen such a pained look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s quite sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old age beats even you,\Nonce renowned as the god of Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that…?!\NWhat the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is that youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it so sudden you can’t tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s me. Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you completed that\NForbidden Jutsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a truly frightening,\Ninhuman monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as you guys go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let you get away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone makes mistakes\Nlt’s nothing to be ashamed about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let this scar be for naught\NWalk with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, breathe in the air\NLift your face to the sky and jump
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:22:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it rains, take a break\NGo where the wind takes you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many regrets\NDon’t let this scar be for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go carve the badges in our chest\NYes, it’s Show Time, life begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone makes mistakes\N It’s nothing to be ashamed about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let this scar be for naught\NWalk with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform sadness into the wind\Nand continue to forge on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forge on strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.43,0:23:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a genius Ninja who appeared\Nduring the war-torn era
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and one of a kind in decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to believe that this individual\Nwould succeed my strength and will.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my naiveté created this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.05,0:23:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bury you now and\Ncorrect my old mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, “A Mistake from the Past:\NA Face Revealed!”
